snippet: Former French Open champion Ana Ivanovic announced her retirement from tennis at the age of 29 on Wednesday because she no longer feels fit enough to compete at the highest level....
lead_paragraph: Former French Open champion Ana Ivanovic announced her retirement from tennis at the age of 29 on Wednesday because she no longer feels fit enough to compete at the highest level.

headline.main: Former World Number One Ivanovic Retires at Age 29
headline.print_headline: Former World Number One Ivanovic Retires at Age 29
